international market by exporting more name-brand products and
contracting more overseas engineering projects, the decision added.
</P>
<P>
In a speech at the meeting, the president of the People's Bank
of China's Shanghai branch, Mao Yingliang, urged local bankers to
fully understand the importance of the government's efforts to
maintain an appropriate rate of economic growth.
</P>
<P>
The national goal for economic growth is expected at eight
percent this year, he noted. 
