<HEADLINE> OPEC Oil Prices Rebound Slowly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Vienna, April 27 (Xinhua) -- The average price of OPEC's basket
of seven crudes increased slightly last week, moving from 12.63
U.S. dollars from the week before to 12.78 dollars, Vienna-based
OPEC Secretariat announced Monday.
</P>
