March and 12.78 dollars for February. It is even considerably
farther from last year's average price of 18.68 dollars.
</P>
<P>
OPEC has set the benchmark price of oil per barrel at 21
U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
The organization uses the average price of OPEC's basket of
seven crudes to monitor the change of oil prices worldwide.
