negative attitude toward Turkey's bid for membership of the
European Union (EU).
</P>
<P>
Turkey has repeatedly said that Germany's position in this
regard is a major obstacle to Turkey's drive to enter the EU,
which excluded Turkey from the enlargement process at a European
summit last December.
</P>
<P>
