(STII) lost 19.81 points to close at 1,471.47 points on Monday.
</P>
<P>
Dealers said that weakening Asian currencies and a dearth of
market-moving incentives kept many players on the sidelines.
Persistent concerns over the impact of the regional financial
turmoil and economic downturn on local companies continued to
discourage investors, they added.
</P>
<P>
