<HEADLINE> Eritrea to Introduce Market Exchange Rates </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, April 27 (Xinhua) -- The Bank of Eritrea has
announced that all foreign currency exchange will be based on
market determined rates effective May 1, 1998.
</P>
<P>
