(ANC)'s National Executive Committee following a request by the
British Labor Party and Sinn Fein, the political wing of the
Irish Republican Army (IRA).
</P>
<P>
The South African delegation will include Former ANC
secretary-general Cyril Ramaphosa, Constitutional Development
Minister Mohamed Valli Moosa, Transport Minister Mac Maharaj and
Premier of Mpumalanga Province Mathews Phosa, ANC National
Chairman Patrick Lekota was quoted as saying.
</P>
