provide an opportunity for the public to participate in crime
prevention by providing an alternative channel for them to give
clues and information on crimes.
</P>
<P>
The website, which can be accessed at
'wwww.internetpolice.ksc.net', will also provide information on
the telephone numbers of all police stations in Thailand, laws
concerning the public safety, and police policy on public security
measures. 
